  <div id="about-bubble" style="display:none">
    <img class="shot" src="shot3.png" alt="" />
    <h1 id="about-bubble-handle">web.reload!</h1>
    <p>
      script.aculo.us provides you with<br/>
      <b>easy-to-use</b>, <b>cross-browser</b> user<br/>
      interface <b>JavaScript libraries</b> to make<br/>
      your web sites and web applications fly.<br/><br/>
      What's inside? <a href="http://madrobby.github.com/scriptaculous/combination-effects-demo/">animation framework</a>,<br/>
      <a href="http://madrobby.github.com/scriptaculous/draggable/">drag and drop</a>, 
      <a href="http://madrobby.github.com/scriptaculous/controls/">Ajax controls</a><br/>
      <a href="http://madrobby.github.com/scriptaculous/builder/">DOM utilities</a>, and <a href="http://madrobby.github.com/scriptaculous/unit-testing/">unit testing</a>.<br/>
      <br/>
      It's an add-on to the<br/>
      fantastic <a href="http://prototypejs.org/">Prototype</a><br/>
      framework.
    </p>
  </div>
  
